    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Power Snooze</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By ANNE GLUSKER</byline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>What are all those nonstop, super-stressed go-getters doing with their weekends this summer? Ask someone on a Monday morning, and chances are you'll get the triumphant response "Took a nap."</p>
        <p>Apparently, no one is in a rush to get to the beach to absorb ultraviolet rays, hiking just invites ticks, and tennis is too sweaty. For people with small children, a daytime snooze is indeed an accomplishment.</p>
      </block>
